                       </div>\n                    <div class=\"town-title\"><h3>Annuity<br> Component</h3></div>\n                    <div class=\"town-text\"><p>The security of a consistent salary doesn’t have to disappear in retirement. Our approach includes an annuity that provides a steady income stream you can rely on. This income is regularly direct-deposited into your bank account and works alongside with other sources like PPF, PF, NPS to cover your everyday expenses.  </p></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"lower-content\">\n                                        <div class=\"single-item\">\n                        <div class=\"icon-box\">\n                        \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"flaticon-mail\"></i>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t                        </div>\n                        <h6>Of City Council</h6>\n                        <p>Of City Council</p>\n                    </div>\n                                        <div class=\"link te-btn\">\n                        <a href=\"\" class=\"te-thm-btn\"><span>Read More</span></a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        \n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e92dfbd elementor-widget elementor-widget-counsolve_icon_box\" data-id=\"e92dfbd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;btn_margin&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;top&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;right&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;bottom&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;left&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;isLinked&quot;:true},&quot;btn_margin_tablet&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;top&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;right&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;bottom&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;left&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;isLinked&quot;:true},&quot;btn_margin_mobile&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;top&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;right&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;bottom&quot;:&quot;&quot;,